data.description: Walk into your well maintained 3 bed, 2 bath home in quiet Chaparral Mesa. 10-panel owned SOLAR system installed for 166% electric offset in 2021 with 20 year warranty. Ring doorbell and EcoBee smart thermostat. NEW CARPET and fresh paint throughout. Partial-open kitchen features granite countertops, under cabinet lighting, stainless steel appliances (including the fridge!) pantry, breakfast bar/ peninsula, extra deep sink, and tons of counter and cabinet space. Large informal dining room. Spacious living room with GAS LOG FIREPLACE. Primary bedroom includes oversized walk-in closet with double shelving. Ensuite with walk-in shower, dual vanities and linen cabinet. Enjoy mountain views in this west facing backyard from the 50 ft long patio, partially covered. Raised garden bed, producing apple tree, shrubs and grass on Smart Home sprinkler system, brick fire pit and plumbed in Blackstone grill. 8x12 shed to house all the yard maintenance tools included! PLUS Lighted flag pole, owned water softener, water heater re-circulator,
